Welcome to 10 Lorne Lane, North Berwick!

Exquisite views, luxurious furnishings and every modern comfort await you in this recently renovated 3bedroom, 2-bathroom beachfront home. Situated in historic North Berwick and within walking distance of world famous golf courses, shopping, dining and a regular rail link into Edinburgh. We call the place Homeland, (it’s a long story) and it is without doubt the most breathtaking and luxurious rental property in the area.
